  "body": "Teku currently keeps all non-finalized states in memory.  When finalization is delayed, this significantly increases memory requirements, often leading to out of memory errors.\r\n\r\nTeku should limit the number of states it keeps in memory and handle regenerating non-finalized states when required.\r\n",
